{{Top|leg}}
'''Baragwinian''' was the main [[Language/Legends|language]] used by the [[Baragwin/Legends|Baragwin]] [[Species/Legends|species]], aside from [[Galactic Basic Standard/Legends|Galactic Basic Standard]].

The Baragwin themselves, however, were not especially fond of this language. Most of them only learned Basic or the languages used on whatever [[Planet/Legends|planet]] they were born, so Baragwinian was not very common. Baragwinian was still considered useful as a [[Trade language/Legends|trade language]], however.

{{Language-stub}}

==Behind the scenes==
Contrary to the description in [[The Bounty Hunters: Scoundrel's Wages|''Scoundrel's Wages'']], the ''[[Ultimate Alien Anthology]]'' claims that there is no native Baragwinian language&mdash;or, at least, that typical Baragwin characters speak only Basic.

